        {
            "_id": "N0g5xdIF3LC3JDxP",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Alchemical Rupture",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a noxious needler takes physical damage from a critical hit or is affected by a shatter spell, one glass chamber within its body shatters, spewing alchemical liquid in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5]. Roll on the alchemical chambers list to determine which one shatters—on a roll of 1–5, creatures in the area take 10d6 damage of the appropriate type (DC 28 basic Reflex). On a roll of 6, creatures must instead save against the sickness effect.</p>\n<table class=\"pf2e\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/br 1d6 #Alchemical Rupture]]</th>\n<th>Alchemical Effect</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>\n<p>@Damage[10d6[acid]] damage @Check[type:reflex|dc:28|basic:true|traits:acid]</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>@Damage[10d6[cold]] damage @Check[type:reflex|dc:28|basic:true|traits:cold]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>@Damage[10d6[electricity]] damage @Check[type:reflex|dc:28|basic:true|traits:electricity]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>@Damage[10d6[fire]] damage @Check[type:reflex|dc:28|basic:true|traits:fire]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>@Damage[10d6[poison]] damage @Check[type:reflex|dc:28|basic:true|traits:poison]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>Sickness: @Check[type:fortitude|dc:26|name:Alchemical Sickness|traits:disease] save or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
                },
